featured_reviews.review_id:
Its an small mosque near badarpur bus stand. After deboarding the bus, you may offer namaz there, its approx. 300 metre from bus stop & its on the main road, lot many vendors sell fruit nd vegetables Nearby choti masjid.
As namaz is farz, so a muslim must stop at the namaz time and offer obligatory namaz then proceed to their work.
